name: LG - 26.2 Cu. Ft. French Door Smart Refrigerator with Dual Ice Maker
typeDescription: Now you can keep your refrigerator organized instead of just wishing you could. description: Stock-up and store everything you need. name: LG - 27 Cu. Ft. Side-by-Side Smart Refrigerator with Craft Ice and InstaView
typeDescription: Express your stylish side or let your organized side have it all—either way, capture your best side in LG's side-by-side InstaView refrigerator with Craft Ice.

typeDescription: Samsung's new Smart Dial Washer with FlexWash™ lets you wash two separate loads at the same time or independently with two washers in the same unit. name: Cuisinart - PerfectTemp 14 Cup Coffeemaker
typeDescription: Turn up the flavor and the temperature on your coffee with the Cuisinart 14 Cup Programmable Coffeemaker! Using our cutting edge coffee technology

name: BISSELL - Little Green ProHeat Corded Handheld Deep Cleaner
typeDescription: Not every mess calls for a full-size carpet cleaning machine. BISSELL® Little Green® ProHeat® portable deep cleaner is a lightweight and compact machine that permanently removes tough spots and stains with the power of OXY

And this portable deep cleaner doesn’t just clean up after pets, it helps save them! BISSELL proudly supports BISSELL Pet Foundation® and its mission to help save homeless pets. When you buy a BISSELL product, you help save pets, too. We’re proud to design products that help make pet messes, odors and pet homelessness disappear.

name: Breville - Juice Fountain® Cold Electric Juicer
typeDescription: The Breville Juice Fountain cold electric juicer is powerful and efficient. The 850W, two-speed motor generates up to 13,000 rpm, processing even the toughest fruits and vegetables in less than a second. The Breville Juice Fountain cold electric juicer features cold spin technology that lets you make fresh, healthy juice full of vitamins and minerals.
description: Two speeds juice a variety of produceUse the slow speed to juice soft fruits and vegetables, such as peaches, strawberries, oranges and kale. The higher speed juices items, such as carrots, apples, beets and gingerroot.Durable, dependable blades easily grind skins and rindsMesh filter and blade assembly ensures long-lasting performance, while retaining the many micro-nutrients in fruit and vegetable peels.
